      <title>泰国赌场计划在公开听证会上赢得了压倒性的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/thai-casino-plan-wins-overwhelming-support-in-public-hearing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[公开听证会上的绝大多数受访者都支持泰国使赌场合法化的计划，政府表明，它愿意合并建议以减轻当地人的高入口障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/thai-casino-plan-wins-overwhelming-support-in-public-hearing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 03:20:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>诺伊姆游览萨尔瓦多监狱住房移民美国被驱逐出境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/noem-to-tour-el-salvador-prison-housing-migrants-the-us-deported</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国土安全部部长克里斯蒂·诺姆（Kristi Noem）将访问萨尔瓦多，哥伦比亚和墨西哥，以突出特朗普政府的边界和移民镇压，包括访问美国在那里飞来飞去的萨尔瓦多住房移民的臭名昭著的设施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/noem-to-tour-el-salvador-prison-housing-migrants-the-us-deported</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 02:44:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>忠诚度测试等待英国在大臣至关重要的一周中的劳动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/loyalty-test-awaits-uk-s-labour-in-crucial-week-for-chancellor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雷切尔·里夫斯（Rachel Reeves）本周将面对一场战斗，以避免在自己的政党内部发生异议，因为英国的国库总理准备宣布数十亿英镑的支出削减。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/loyalty-test-awaits-uk-s-labour-in-crucial-week-for-chancellor</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国对家庭用餐的胃口不太可能发生通货膨胀威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/british-appetite-for-home-dining-poses-unlikely-inflation-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国的竞争性杂货行业倾向于确保食品保持相对便宜，但是，尽管谈到一场超市价格战，但随着通货膨胀率上升，购物者仍面临奇怪的情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/british-appetite-for-home-dining-poses-unlikely-inflation-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 00:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊拉克在关于浮动气码头的会谈中，以弥合电源差距</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/iraq-in-talks-over-floating-gas-terminals-to-bridge-power-gap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊拉克正在与几家公司进行会谈，以便在6月初之前确保两个浮动存储重新设备，因为欧佩克的第二大生产商试图解决由美国对伊朗的举动造成的电力短缺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/iraq-in-talks-over-floating-gas-terminals-to-bridge-power-gap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 23:37:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Yoon等待裁决时，韩国法院恢复了PM</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/south-korea-s-court-to-rule-on-pm-han-s-impeachment-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国法院推翻了总理汉德斯 - 苏（Han Duck-Soo）的弹each，恢复了代理领导人，因为该国等待对尤恩·苏克·尤尔（Yoon Suk Yeol）总统的政治命运的单独判决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/south-korea-s-court-to-rule-on-pm-han-s-impeachment-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 23:18:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>致命的以色列罢工一半哈马斯在加沙的顶级领导</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/lethal-israeli-strikes-halve-hamas-top-leadership-in-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[双方说，以色列在加沙地带上杀死了哈马斯的两名事实上的内阁成员，在一个重新的以色列进攻中，旨在将巴勒斯坦派系摧毁作为军事和统治部队的旨在摧毁巴勒斯坦派系时，在20人的论坛中丧生。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/lethal-israeli-strikes-halve-hamas-top-leadership-in-gaza</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 22:49:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰，美国在利雅得举行的会谈，以争取广泛停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/ukraine-us-talks-start-in-riyadh-kyiv-s-defense-chief-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰人和美国官员在利雅得举行了会谈，随着唐纳德·特朗普总统推动停火，恢复了俄罗斯全面入侵的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/ukraine-us-talks-start-in-riyadh-kyiv-s-defense-chief-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 16:03:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议员说，中国必须在美国贸易谈判之前修复芬太尼流。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/china-must-fix-fentanyl-flow-before-us-trade-talks-senator-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据参议院的唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）盟友称，中国需要采取行动，以阻止芬太尼前体向美国的流动，然后再对贸易进行交谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/china-must-fix-fentanyl-flow-before-us-trade-talks-senator-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 14:25:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚司库听起来我们对我们的“地震”冲击警报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/australia-treasurer-warns-of-seismic-us-global-economic-shock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚的财务主管吉姆·查尔默斯（Jim Chalmers）警告说，新的美国政府的政策将对全球经济产生“地震”影响，这是在周二发放的国家预算之前。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/australia-treasurer-warns-of-seismic-us-global-economic-shock</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 22:40:18 GMT</pubDate>
